# ============================================================================
# Arda-Specific Notes
# ============================================================================
# 1. Arda uses production MDSO for both dev and prod environments
# 2. Arda has specific Hydra keys: ARDA_ADVA_RAD, ARDA_NOC, etc.
# 3. Optional Sentry integration via SENTRY_DNS variable
#
# Security Notes:
# 1. All passwords and sensitive keys are encrypted using Fernet
# 2. Each encrypted value requires a corresponding _SKELLY decryption key
# 3. To generate a Fernet key: python -c "from cryptography.fernet import Fernet; print(Fernet.generate_key().decode())"
# ============================================================================
